description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of The Haven and Rookstone House to provide 46 residential units comprising 27 x 4 bedroom houses, 7 x 1 bedroom flats, 6 x 2 Bedroom flats and 6 x 3 bedroom flats, together with 71 car parking spaces, cycle parking provision, refuse and recycling provision, a relocated vehicular access to Springfield Road and landscaping and associated works
